#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn17:2.11.4"
msgid "‘Kathaṃ carahi taṃ, deva, samudācarāmī’ti? "
msgstr "‘Then how exactly, Your Majesty, am I to speak to you?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn17:2.11.5"
msgid "‘Evaṃ kho maṃ tvaṃ, devi, samudācara: "
